# Xcode
#
# gitignore contributors: remember to update Global/Xcode.gitignore, Objective-C.gitignore & Swift.gitignore

## User-specific
*.xcuserdatad
*.xcscmblueprint

## Xcode 8 and later
*.xccheckout
*.xcworkspace
!default.xcworkspace

## Google Services (Firebase)
GoogleService-Info.plist

## Dependencies
Packages/
Package.resolved
.swiftpm/
.build/

## Misc
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.lock

## Artifacts
DerivedData/
build/
*.xcresult
